high_descs: walk to the front of the black table just ahead
grab a knife off of the table
turn around and walk to the end of the kitchen counter tops on your left
put the knife inside of the pullout drawer there
turn around and walk over to the left side of the black table on your right
pick up the second knife off of the table there
turn around and walk over to the end of the kitchen counter tops on your left
place the knife in the same drawer as the other knife went into
anns.task_desc: place two knifes in the kitchen drawer

high_descs: Walk to the other side of the black round table to face the tea pot.
Pick up the yellow knife next to the green sponge on top of the table.
Walk to the right and go to the first cabinet that has a toaster on top of it.
Open the drawer of the cabinet, put the knife in it and close the drawer.
Turn around, walk straight to the wall, turn right to go back to the black round table.
Pick up another yellow knife next to the apple.
Go back to the drawer of the cabinet with a toaster on top of it.
Open the drawer, put the other knife next to the first knife and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 yellow knives from the round black table to the drawer of the cabinet with a toaster.

high_descs: Move to the dining table in front of you.
Pick up a knife from the table.
Move to the left side of the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the drawer and place the knife inside.
Move to the dining table to the left of you.
Pick up a knife from the table.
Move to the left side of the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the drawer and place the knife inside.
anns.task_desc: Put two knives from the dining table in the drawer to the left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn right to face the black table.
Pick the knife up off of the black table.
Turn around, go to the left and open the drawer at the end of the counter.
Place the knife in the drawer and close it.
Turn around and head right to face the other side of the black table.
Pick the yellow knife up off of the black table.
Turn to the right then to the left to face the drawer at the end of the counter.
Open the drawer and place the knife inside of it.
anns.task_desc: Place both knives inside of the drawer at the end of the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left then walk straight and face the right black round table
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the table
Turn around walk straight then turn left at the counter next to the refrigerator and face it
Open the top drawer and place the knife inside
Turn around walk straight then turn right and face the black round table
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the table
Turn right then walk straight and then turn left and face the counter left of the refrigerator
Open the top drawer and place the knife inside
anns.task_desc: Putting away yellow handled knives in the drawer

high_descs: Back up, turn to the left, turn to the right, go to the dining table.
Pick up the big knife that is on the table between the teapot and sponges.
Turn around and go forward, turn left and go to the drawer between the fridge and stove.
Open the drawer, put the knife in the drawer and close the drawer.
Turn around, go to the wall, hang a right, go to the wall, turn right to the dining table.
Pick up the big knife that is in front of the lettuce on the table.
Turn right and go forward, turn left and go to the drawer between the fridge and stove.
Open the drawer, put the knife in the drawer, close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two knives in a drawer.
